rulesText:
Clan Rules
**Rule 1** -  Teleporting any random player or enemy player (even friends) to a gang/main clan base or a team member is strictly prohibited and will be punished.

**Rule 2**-  New recruits will not have access to the community base until they earn the Member role.

**Rule 3**-  Self-Griefing or by teleporting  an enemy is considered betrayal and will most likely result in a ban.

**Rule 4**- Gang leaders cannot make alliance decisions without permission.

**Rule 5**-  Betrayal will lead to blacklisting, a permanent ban (unless a sincere apology is made), and bounty hunting.

**Rule 6**- Sub Gang leaders cannot kick or ban members without a valid reason and must inform TysonBlade or Hep1s and awa_nb

**Rule 7**- Infighting: the one who initiates an attack will face severe consequences (up to expulsion). Misunderstandings can be resolved, but even accidental attacks earn a warning. 

**Rule 8** - Everyone must be treated equally, whether combatant, grinder, recruiter, or leader.

**Rule 9** - No trash talking or provoking teammates.

**Rule 10**- No team killing; doing so will result in penalties.

**Rule 11**- No yoinking shulker boxes, even as a joke.

**Rule 12** - No begging clan members for tp to their PRIVATE
bases.       If anyone leaks coords of a private base to another clan members without permission of the base owner, there will be a penalty or possible demotion.

**Rule 13** - Threats like leaking base coordinates will not be tolerated.

**Rule 14** - Dropping in ENVOYS without leader command will result in penalties and possible demotion.

**Rule 15** - Disrespecting leaders or members (through killing, abuse, or insults) will result in a 1-week suspension from the clan
